## 1. Product Vision & Overview\
\
### 1.1 One-Liner\
\
**SendMo makes shipping between people effortless \'e2\'80\'94 no more exchanging addresses or figuring out shipping costs.**\
\
### 1.2 Marketing Taglines\
\
- "Get it delivered to you"\
- "When you need something delivered to you"\
- "Shareable shipping label links that help you get things delivered to you"\
- "Make it easy for people to ship things to you \'e2\'80\'94 marketplace purchases, returned items, and more"\
\
**For Senders/Sellers:**\
- "Marketplace sellers: SendMo enables buyers to create and pay for the shipping label, so you can get the product out the door"\
\
### 1.3 The Problem\
\
Shipping between individuals is unnecessarily complicated:\
\
1. **Address exchange**: Recipients have to share their address with every sender \'e2\'80\'94 privacy concern and friction.\
2. **Cost confusion**: Senders have to figure out box sizes, carrier options, and costs.\
3. **Back-and-forth**: Both parties go back and forth on shipping estimates.\
4. **No visibility**: Neither party has visibility once the package is in transit.\
\
### 1.4 The Solution\
\
**SendMo Label Links.** Recipients create a link once, share it with anyone who needs to send them something. Senders click, enter package details, and print a label. Done.\
\
**Two simple steps:**\
1. Configure your shipping label link\
2. Share it with the sender for them to finalize and print\
\
### 1.5 Value Proposition\
\
| Audience | Value |\
|----------|-------|\
| **Recipients** | Control over shipping \'e2\'80\'94 set preferences once, share a link, receive packages. No more sending your address to everyone. |\
| **Senders** | Dead simple shipping \'e2\'80\'94 click a link, enter package info, print label, drop off. No address lookup, no rate shopping, no guesswork. |\
| **Privacy** | Recipients can keep their address private until the label is printed. |\
\
### 1.6 How SendMo Makes Money\
\
```\
Display Price = EasyPost Rate \'c3\'97 1.15  (Standard \'e2\'80\'94 15% margin)\
Display Price = EasyPost Rate \'c3\'97 1.10  (With SendMo Balance \'e2\'80\'94 10% margin)\
```\
\
- The SendMo fee is **never shown separately** \'e2\'80\'94 users see a single "Shipping" price.\
- Upsell: "Save 5% on shipping with a SendMo Balance" \'e2\'86\'92 Coming soon post-MVP.\
