## 2. Key Concepts & Terminology\
\
### 2.1 Core Terms\
\
| Term | Definition |\
|------|------------|\
| **Recipient** | Person receiving the package. Creates and owns SendMo links. Pays for shipping. |\
| **Sender** | Person shipping the package. Clicks the link, enters package details, prints label. Does NOT pay. |\
| **SendMo Link** | A shareable URL (e.g., `sendmo.co/s/k8Hj2mNp4x`) that enables shipping to a recipient. |\
| **Label Link** | A type of SendMo Link that generates a printable shipping label for the sender. |\
| **Price Cap** | Maximum shipping cost the recipient is willing to pay (default: $100). |\
| **Card Hold** | An authorization hold placed on the recipient's payment method when a label is created. |\
\
### 2.2 Types of SendMo Links (MVP + Future)\
\
| Type | Description | Address Visible to Sender? | MVP? |\
|------|-------------|---------------------------|------|\
| **Label Link (Flexible)** | Reusable link with default settings. Sender configures package details. | Yes (on printed label) | \'e2\'9c\'85 |\
| **Label Link (One-Time)** | Pre-configured for specific shipment. Fixed package size, origin area, etc. | Yes (on printed label) | \'e2\uc0\u157 \'8c |\
| **Private Shipment Link** | Sender gets QR code instead of label. Must drop off at carrier location. | No | \'e2\uc0\u157 \'8c |\
\
**MVP focuses exclusively on Flexible Label Links.**\
\
### 2.3 Link Configuration (Recipient Controls)\
\
**Basic Settings:**\
- **Ship-to address**: Defaults to primary address (private, only shown on label)\
- **Speed preference**: Any / Economy / Standard / Express (default: Any)\
- **Price cap**: Maximum shipping cost (default: $100)\
\
**Advanced Settings (Collapsible):**\
- **Preferred carrier**: Any / USPS / UPS / FedEx (default: Any)\
- **Insurance**: On/Off (default: Off, adds ~$3\'e2\'80\'935 to cost)\
\
### 2.4 Link States\
\
| State | Description | Sender Experience |\
|-------|-------------|-------------------|\
| **Pending** | Link created but payment method not added or not verified | Sender sees "This link is pending payment. Contact [Recipient] to complete setup." |\
| **Active** | Payment authorized, link ready for use | Sender can complete full flow and print label |\
| **Paused** | Recipient manually paused the link | Sender sees "This link is currently paused." |\
| **Deactivated** | Recipient permanently deactivated | Sender sees 404-style "Link not found" |\
