## 3. Target Users & Use Cases\
\
### 3.1 Primary Users: Recipients\
\
- **Marketplace buyers** (Facebook Marketplace, Craigslist, OfferUp) who need sellers to ship items\
- **Office managers / administrators** who need employees, vendors, or customers to send documents/items\
- **Frequent travelers** who left items at hotels/Airbnbs\
- **Anyone** who wants a simpler way to receive shipped items without sharing their address repeatedly\
\
**B2B Use Case**: SendMo is effectively a **pre-paid label system** for businesses. An office manager shares their link with vendors, remote employees, or customers who need to send items to the office.\
\
### 3.2 Secondary Users: Senders\
\
- Marketplace sellers\
- Friends/family sending items\
- Hotels returning forgotten items\
- Employees/vendors sending to a business\
- Anyone who needs to ship something to someone\
\
