| What is SendMo? | SendMo lets you create a personal shipping label link. Share it with anyone who needs to send you something \'e2\'80\'94 they get a pre-paid label instantly, and you control the cost, carrier, and destination. |\
| Who pays for shipping? | You (the recipient) pay for shipping. When you set up your link, you add a payment method and set a price cap. The sender never has to pay anything. |\
| How does SendMo make money? | SendMo adds a small convenience fee on top of carrier rates. There are no subscription fees or hidden charges. |\
| Is my address visible to the sender? | No. Your address is only printed on the label itself. The sender never sees your full address in the app \'e2\'80\'94 they just print and ship. |\
