| Can I use SendMo for international shipping? | Not yet \'e2\'80\'94 SendMo currently supports domestic US shipping only. International support is on our roadmap. |\
| How do I get tracking updates? | You'll receive tracking updates via email as soon as the sender drops off the package. Real-time tracking is available in your dashboard. |\
